>Description:
If the DrScheme window is made small enough that the buttons in the bar at the top don't fit, then the scroll bar for the definitions window disappears.  Note that this happens on my monitor for almost any window size less that fullscreen.
>How-To-Repeat:
1. Shrink window until buttons at top don't fit.
2. Bye-bye scrollbar.
